## The Announcement

She turns to face the tower. Her voice carries further than it should:

> *"Attention. Two new climbers have been registered. By order of the Tower's standing provisions, they are hereby designated as Special-Class Climbers. The following provisions apply:*
>
> *One — Companions of Special-Class Climbers have their level synchronized to match the Climber's current level at time of entry.*
>
> *Two — Special-Class Climbers may form a party of five, rather than the standard four.*
>
> *Three — Strength gained within the Tower persists outside of it.*
>
> *Four — Special-Class Climbers retain all skills, experience, and class features gained on any floor, regardless of floor reset conditions.*
>
> *Five — Items marked as Tower-Bound may be carried out by Special-Class Climbers.*
>
> *This announcement has been logged."*

She steps back. Says nothing else.

