Shortly after the players arrive at the center, they hear footsteps from the east path.

> *Four figures emerge from the mist — each wearing a different style of gear, all of them clearly as new as you are. The one in front raises a hand in greeting.*

**The Moonlight Squad:**

| Member | Name | Class | Personality |
|---|---|---|---|
